params.sqlcmd: "select " +" TO_CHAR(SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CONFIRM_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD hh24:mi:ss') as \\"CONFIRM_DATE\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"LOG_CD\\" as \\"LOG_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD hh24:mi:ss') as \\"CREATED_DATE\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"BUSINESS_NAME\\" as \\"BUSINESS_NAME\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_BY\\" as \\"CREATED_BY\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"MSG\\" as \\"MSG\\", " +" TRANSLATE(SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"DATA_STRING\\", CHR(10), '／') as \\"DATA_STRING\\", " +" M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_NAME\\" as \\"PLANT_NAME\\", " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_NAME\\" as \\"USER_NAME\\" " +"from " +" SYS_MSG_LOG, " +" M_PLANT, " +" USER_MST " +"where " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_CD\\"(+) " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_BY\\" = USER_MST.\\"USER_CD\\"(+) " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_DATE\\" >= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD hh24:mi:ss') " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_DATE\\" < TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD hh24:mi:ss') " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"BUSINESS_NAME\\" like ? " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_BY\\" = ? " +"order by " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"LOG_CD\\" desc, " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_DATE\\" desc " +""

"select " +" TO_CHAR(SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CONFIRM_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD hh24:mi:ss') as \\"CONFIRM_DATE\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"LOG_CD\\" as \\"LOG_CD\\", " +" TO_CHAR(SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_DATE\\", 'YYYY/MM/DD hh24:mi:ss') as \\"CREATED_DATE\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"BUSINESS_NAME\\" as \\"BUSINESS_NAME\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_BY\\" as \\"CREATED_BY\\", " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"MSG\\" as \\"MSG\\", " +" TRANSLATE(SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"DATA_STRING\\", CHR(10), '／') as \\"DATA_STRING\\", " +" M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_NAME\\" as \\"PLANT_NAME\\", " +" USER_MST.\\"USER_NAME\\" as \\"USER_NAME\\" " +"from " +" SYS_MSG_LOG, " +" M_PLANT, " +" USER_MST " +"where " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_CD\\"(+) " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_BY\\" = USER_MST.\\"USER_CD\\"(+) " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"LOG_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" COUNT(1) " +"from " +" SYS_MSG_LOG, " +" M_PLANT, " +" USER_MST " +"where " +" SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = M_PLANT.\\"PLANT_CD\\"(+) " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_BY\\" = USER_MST.\\"USER_CD\\"(+) " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_DATE\\" >= TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD hh24:mi:ss') " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_DATE\\" < TO_DATE(?, 'YYYY/MM/DD hh24:mi:ss') " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"BUSINESS_NAME\\" like ? " +" and SYS_MSG_LOG.\\"CREATED_BY\\" = ? " +" and ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"
